source.name: OPIC US and Developmental Effects FY 2008
source.description: Analysis of the project's expected impact on U.S. employment and U.S. balance of payments flows. Also includes impact analysis for each project receiving OPIC support in terms of net impact on the economic and social development of the project's host country. The analysis uses objective measurements to demonstrate the developmental impact of OPIC-supported projects.
